

This version adds margin-note style callouts under each answer explaining what pushes it into Proficient territory, plus a summary table at the end mapping Developing vs. Proficient patterns per question,
useful if you want students to self-check before submitting, or want a quick reference when grading against the Complete/Redo model.

Create a text or markdown file called "Spring 1 Reflection" that answers these three questions:
1. What actually runs right now?
2. What's still missing or broken?
3. Are you still on track with the scope from your charter, or has anything changed?


